# python_cli Profile

## Purpose

Use this profile for a Python command-line project that uses src/, tests/, pytest, and a CLI smoke check.

## Recommended Layout

- src/
- tests/
- docs/
- AGENTS.override.md

## Verification Model

- pytest is the default test runner.
- CLI smoke verifies the primary user-facing command path.
- Acceptance trace records which requirement each test or smoke result supports.

## P1 Boundary

This profile template does not create Python source code, tests, packaging files, or scripts. Those belong to later project-specific phases.

## Safety Notes

Use synthetic fixtures. Do not commit private raw input, secrets, local environment dumps, or real service tokens.
